Description: Interactive TUI dashboard for shortwave listeners
 SWL Schedule Tool provides an interactive terminal dashboard and CLI tools
 for querying the EiBi shortwave broadcast schedule database. Features
 include real-time ON AIR detection, bearing and distance from your
 QTH, station detail modals, and integrated schedule updates.
